 proven methods of revenue-generating strategies. For example, if you want to generate more leads, your consultant should suggest a design that puts your business&#39;s phone number front and center on your site.","<strong>How often do you update SEO? </strong>You need to ensure your website lists high on search engines. And to do so, someone needs to update keywords and content as algorithms change. Find out whether this is on your shoulders, or if the company takes care of it for you – and if they do, how much is that going to cost you each month?","<strong>What do you need from me? </strong>Typically, a web design company has access to stock photos, but it&#39;s your business and you may have images, articles and more that you want to incorporate in the website&#39;s design. Find out what you need to send to the web design company so your design isn&#39;t delayed.","<strong>What if I don&#39;t like it? </strong>Most web design companies work with you every step of the way and get your approval on various design elements before it all comes together. There&#39;s no guarantee, though, that you&#39;ll like the result. Find out if you&#39;ll be charged for changes as they work toward a design you like.","<strong>What&#39;s included in the price you&#39;re quoting me? </strong>It&#39;s important to get the full picture of what you&#39;re getting before you sign on the proverbial dotted line. You don&#39;t want to get a surprise bill for marketing or maintenance at the end of the month.","<strong>Who takes care of maintenance? </strong>This comes down to what&#39;s more important to you: time or money. If you&#39;d rather maintain the content on your site, make sure the web design company offers a CMS that your team can use to update articles, blogs and images. Otherwise, find out how much it&#39;s going to cost you to have the web design business to maintain your site and social media, if it&#39;s available.","<strong>What about hosting? </strong>Find out whether you need to secure a domain name and web host or if the web design company takes care of that for you, and what the cost is.","<strong>Who owns the website and content? </strong>This is especially important to know if you plan to migrate to another web design company. If you own the website once all is said and done, it will be of little consequence.","<strong>How will I know if my website is successful? </strong>Ideally, you&#39;ll know your new site is successful based on increased business, but a web design company should also offer various analytics to show you in black and white how they&#39;ve helped improve your numbers."],"type":"ol"},"id":"e5d966bd-07dc-4222-8011-c06446bb94ed","type":"list"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["When you&#39;re ready to upgrade your current website or change your brand, there&#39;s a web design company out there that suits your business&#39;s needs. Be sure to do a bit of the legwork before a consultation so you can answer questions about what you want to achieve with your new website, whether it&#39;s increased sales, easier management, better design, longer stays by visitors to your site, or overall increased traffic."]},"id":"26bb845b-8263-4ddd-9a4d-3c9297556c48","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"bc517ecb-e479-4c2c-849c-8e9f074f368e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/internet/web-site-design/rfqz/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788\">Blue Fountain Media</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/internet/web-site-design/rfqz/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788\">Big Drop</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/internet/web-site-design/rfqz/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788\">Webvanta</a>","<a href=\"http://lp.webimax.com/website-design-services/?utm_source=Review%20Site&utm_medium=Banner&utm_campaign=Web%20Design&utm_content=&campaignid=&adgroupid=&utm_term={keyword}&leadsource=TopTenReviews.com\">WebiMax</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/internet/web-